534,-0.0171,-0.0149,-0.0167,0.1235,0.0337]},{"referencia":"Período de Teste (2026), Glossário da Reforma Tributária","lei":"Glossário da Reforma Tributária","artigo":null,"paragrafo":null,"texto":"Período de Teste (2026): Fase inicial e experimental de cobrança do IBS e da CBS, em 2026, destinada a testar os sistemas e procedimentos da reforma sem gerar carga tributária adicional para o contribuinte. Nesse ano, o IBS é cobrado à alíquota estadual (não municipal) de 0,1% e a CBS à alíquota de 0,9%. Os valores recolhidos são integralmente compensáveis com PIS, Cofins e a contribuição para o PIS/Pasep devidos pelo próprio contribuinte; havendo insuficiência de débitos para compensar, o valor pode ser compensado com qualquer outro tributo federal ou ressarcido em até 60 dias. A arrecadação do IBS nesse período não segue as regras normais de partilha entre entes, sendo destinada, sucessivamente, ao financiamento do Comitê Gestor do IBS e ao Fundo de Compensação de Benefícios Fiscais. Contribuintes que cumprirem as obrigações acessórias podem ser dispensados do recolhimento efetivo. A partir de 2027 inicia-se a cobrança em caráter definitivo da CBS, com extinção progressiva de PIS/Cofins.\nBase legal: Art. 125 (e art. 126) do Ato das Disposições Constitucionais Transitórias, incluído pela EC nº 132/2023.","embedding":[0.0394,0.0043,0.0749,0.0587,-0.0703,0.0213,0.0075,-0.0297,-0.0019,-0.0341,0.0948,0.017,-0.0135,-0.0081,0.0696,-0.0072,-0.0171,0.0121,-0.0384,-0.0334,0.008,0.016,-0.0355,-0.012,0.0051,-0.0988,-0.0891,0.0044,-0.0208,-0.0232,0.1084,0.0005,-0.0285,-0.0549,-0.0192,0.0461,-0.0845,0.024,0.0517,0.047,-0.0217,0.0529,0.0073,-0.0521,-0.0519,0.0267,0.0155,-0.0376,0.0176,0.0646,-0.0076,0.0704,0.0344,-0.0715,-0.0329,0.0265,-0.0388,0.0761,-0.0334,-0.0108,0.0729,-0.0308,-0.011,-0.0298,-0.0768,0.0279,0.0208,0.0839,-0.029,-0.063,-0.0894,0.0882,-0.0066,-0.0762,-0.0011,0.0272,0.0571,-0.0651,0.049,-0.0177,-0.0544,0.0287,-0.016,0.0439,-0.0154,0.0431,-0.0685,0.0301,-0.0254,0.0133,